official_title: Community Support Program for Lung Cancer Screening
inclusion_criteria:
* Upcoming or missed follow-up LDCT (low dose CT)
* West Philadelphia resident
* Between 18-89 years' old
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must have minimum age of 18 Years
Must have maximum age of 89 Years
exclusion_criteria:
* No upcoming LDCT
* Lives outside West Philadelphia
* Outside age range
